long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Welcome to “Just Ben Photography” the Portfolio of Nature, Wildlife and Outdoor Photographer Benjamin Schneider.

Here you have the chance to experience the most stunning Landscapes of Europe and the United States as well as breathtaking close-ups of Wildlife that will show you details you have never seen before!

All my photos are available as Fine Art Prints, Mounted or Framed Fine Art Prints and as Gallery Wraps.
